                        2. <strong class="font-semibold text-burning-flame">Direct Database Access</strong>: You can query your DB directly from your component.</p><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-palladian mt-8 mb-4">Example</h2><p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-oatmeal my-5 font-light">Here is a simple example of a server component fetching data:</p><div class="my-8 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-blue-fantastic/50 shadow-lg bg-[#0F1620]"><div class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-3 bg-blue-fantastic/20 border-b border-blue-fantastic/30 backdrop-blur-sm"><span class="text-xs font-mono text-burning-flame uppercase tracking-wider">tsx</span><div class="flex space-x-1.5"><div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-truffle-trouble/50"></div><div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-burning-flame/50"></div><div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-fantastic/50"></div></div></div><pre class="p-5 overflow-x-auto text-sm font-mono leading-relaxed text-oatmeal"><code>async function NoteList() {
  const notes = await db.notes.getAll();
  return (
    &lt;div&gt;
      {notes.map(note =&gt; (
        &lt;p key={note.id}&gt;{note.title}&lt;/p&gt;
      ))}
    &lt;/div&gt;
  );
}</code></pre></div><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-palladian mt-8 mb-4">Conclusion</h2><p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-oatmeal my-5 font-light">RSC is the future of building high-performance React apps.</p></div></div></article><div class="mt-20 pt-10 border-t border-white/10"><div class="animate-reveal-up paused " style="animation-delay: 0.2s; width: 100%;"><h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-palladian mb-6 flex items-center gap-2"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-zap text-burning-flame" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"></path></svg>Related Transmissions</h3></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6"><div class="animate-reveal-up paused " style="animation-delay: 0.3s; width: 100%;"><div class="cursor-pointer p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-blue-fantastic/10 hover:bg-blue-fantastic/30 hover:border-burning-flame/30 transition-all"><h4 class="font-bold text-palladian mb-2">Mastering Tailwind CSS Grid</h4><p class="text-xs text-oatmeal/50 line-clamp-2 font-mono">Stop fighting with CSS grid. Learn how to use Tailwind utility classes to build complex layouts.</p></div></div></div></div></div>
